<h1 class="title">Clustering Algebra</h1>
<p>
<b>Go to plane of decay products, then boost to P<sub>z</sub> = 0</b>
</p>

<div id="outline-container-orgfbbbf3c" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgfbbbf3c">Start</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgfbbbf3c">
<p>
<b>DOF counting:</b>
</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>\(P_1^\mu\) - 3 DoF : \(P_x\), \(P_z\) and m</li>
<li>\(P_2^\mu\) - 3 DoF : \(P_x\), \(P_z\) and m</li>
<li>1 constraint \(P_z^1 + P_z^2 = 0\)</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org73bd43f" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org73bd43f">End</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org73bd43f">
<p>
One combined vector
</p>

<p>
<b>DOF counting:</b>
</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>\(P_T\), \(\theta\) , z, \(m_1\), \(m_2\)</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org45ca4ae" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org45ca4ae">Clustering</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org45ca4ae">
<p>
\[
P_{comb}^\mu = P_1^\mu + P_2^\mu = \begin{pmatrix} E_1 + E_2 \\ P_T^1 + P_T^2 \\ 0 \\ 0 \end{pmatrix}
\]
</p>
</div>
</div>
